1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science has a clearer story about registered reports than social media does.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:08,400
Registered reports are research plans peer-reviewed before data collection.

3
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:10,400
This means results aren't cherry-picked.

4
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:11,600
Transparency is key.

5
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:15,600
Studies show registered reports can reduce bias and improve reproducibility.

6
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:21,200
In a world full of misinformation, registered reports shine a light on rigorous science.

7
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:24,400
Want to explore more about how science works?

8
